{"tid":1086884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大劉 所有運行光了，便會被麻包套住了","createTime":"2019-04-01T04:49:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T16:50:59.000Z","uid":10090,"like":223,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"cd2a10d16eb9731629a1f17cd1febf9c27682a97","tid":1086884,"uid":10090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T04:49:29.000Z","msg":"華人置業前主席劉鑾雄透過律師行發聲明，指今天已就政府建議的《逃犯條例》修訂，向高等法院申請司法覆核許可。<br />\n劉鑾雄及南華前足主羅傑承因為行賄澳門前運輸工務司司長歐文龍及清洗黑錢罪成，2014年於澳門法院被判入獄5年零3個月，而因為港、澳並無簽訂移交協議，因此兩人未有服刑；一旦政府建議單次個案式移交安排獲得通過，兩人有可能被澳方申請移交至澳門服刑。<br />\n劉鑾雄的兒子、身兼青年發展委員會副主席劉鳴煒早前出席民主黨劉慧卿的網台節目時，曾在回應修例建議時指，聽聞商界有擔憂，但不便談論，並稱：「你又唔係唔識我老豆」、「因為涉及我老豆，我講咩都會無咁中立。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee7f00bcff7b51c869a38abfea87f8bc423c81e5","tid":1086884,"uid":10692,"like":73,"dislike":0,"score":73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T04:50:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ba9788974a652d4df755e722feef23ea97570487","tid":1086884,"uid":10090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T04:56:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"309ceb44e03a0f9d2410bdb61fe1a11db3b087a9","tid":1086884,"uid":79563,"like":125,"dislike":2,"score":123,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T04:56:52.000Z","msg":"大劉 拖到林鄭任期完結, 就有轉機"},{"pid":"088041e8a0f25fcc9531009fff4d7360299a7867","tid":1086884,"uid":22553,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T04:57:21.000Z","msg":"照計咁有錢，一定有好多本護照，立法前一刻著草<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e07f2f12bb4c525f26324f2146c9ff647f0225dc","tid":1086884,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T05:00:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 